milestones.description: Johnston has broken the record for most sixes in an innings (4) in ODIs for IRE, going past John Mooney's 1
Jeremy Bray's 116 is the highest individual score in ODIs (for IRE), surpassing Eoin Morgan's 99
Jeremy Bray has broken the record for most runs in boundaries (64) in an innings in ODIs for IRE, going past Eoin Morgan's 34
Johnston has broken the record for most sixes (4) in ODIs for IRE, going past Eoin Morgan's 1
Jeremy Bray has become the top scorer for IRE in ODIs with 146 runs, going past Kyle McCallan's 120
This is the highest match aggregate (564) involving teams Ireland & Scotland in ODIs
Jeremy Bray and Porterfield's 24-run partnership is IRE's highest for the 1st wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 15 between Jeremy Bray and Porterfield
Jeremy Bray and Kevin O'Brien's 23-run partnership is IRE's highest for the 4th wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 19 between Andre Botha and Eoin Morgan
Kyle McCallan and Jeremy Bray's 51-run partnership is IRE's highest for the 6th wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 22 between Johnston and Eoin Morgan
Colin Smith and Neil McCallum's 104-run partnership is SCOT's highest for the 7th wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 61 between Hamilton and Alec Davies
Andre Botha has broken the record for playing the most ODIs (4) for IRE, going past Jeremy Bray
